  "remarks": "Head of the “Ashiyaneh” cyber group linked with the Iranian regime. “Ashiyaneh” Digital Security, founded by Behrouz Kamalian, is responsible for intensive cyber-attacks on both domestic opponents and reformists and foreign institutions. Kamalian’s “Ashiyaneh” organisation’s work has assisted the regime’s crackdown against the opposition, which has involved numerous serious human rights violations.",
